itHub API 路徑與 GitHub 文件，減少各位在茫茫大海中撈文件：",[39,61,62,75],{},[42,63,64,65],{},"GitHub API 文件\n",[39,66,67],{},[42,68,69],{},[70,71,72],"a",{"href":72,"rel":73},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fcn\u002Frest\u002Freference\u002Fusers",[74],"nofollow",[42,76,77,78],{},"GitHub API 路徑\n",[39,79,80],{},[42,81,82],{},[70,83,84],{"href":84,"rel":85},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002F",[74],[12,87,88],{"id":88},"準備實作",[16,90,91],{},"首先透過上面的需求我們可以了解到我們將會使用 GitHub API 文件取得使用者 Star 過的專案，因此一開始我們必須先閱讀一下 GitHub API 文件。",[93,94,96],"h3",{"id":95},"github-api","GitHub API",[16,98,99,100,104,105,109],{},"基本上上面需求我們可以了解到將會需要使用跟使用者相關的 API，畢竟我們要找使用者按過的 Star 專案，因此在 ",[70,101,102],{"href":102,"rel":103},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fcn\u002Frest\u002F",[74]," 頁面可以看到一個 ",[106,107,108],"strong",{},"用戶"," 的字眼：",[16,111,112],{},"點進去之後在前面看到相關的 AJAX 回傳結果，如下：",[114,115,120],"pre",{"className":116,"code":117,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{\n  \"login\": \"octocat\",\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"node_id\": \"MDQ6VXNlcjE=\",\n  \"avatar_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fimages\u002Ferror\u002Foctocat_happy.gif\",\n  \"gravatar_id\": \"\",\n  \"url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\",\n  \"html_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Foctocat\",\n  \"followers_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Ffollowers\",\n  \"following_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Ffollowing{\u002Fother_user}\",\n  \"gists_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Fgists{\u002Fgist_id}\",\n  \"starred_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Fstarred{\u002Fowner}{\u002Frepo}\",\n  \"subscriptions_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Fsubscriptions\",\n  \"organizations_url\": \"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Foctocat\u002Forgs\",\n  \