"class":126,"line":127},[124,747,131],{"class":130},[124,749,750,752,754,757],{"class":126,"line":134},[124,751,272],{"class":137},[124,753,141],{"class":130},[124,755,756],{"class":144},"\"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fstarred\"",[124,758,148],{"class":130},[124,760,761],{"class":126,"line":151},[124,762,696],{"class":130},[16,764,765,766,771],{},"這樣你就可以直接點上面連結網址打開來查看結果，或者你也可以試著使用 Postman 神器來測試戳一下，如果對於 Postman 不熟悉的話可以閱讀一下",[70,767,770],{"href":768,"rel":769},"https:\u002F\u002Fithelp.ithome.com.tw\u002Farticles\u002F10201503",[74],"這一篇","，因此這邊就不繼續著墨如何使用 Postman 了。",[16,773,774,775,778],{},"那麼透過上面閱讀 API 文件之後，我們可以知道我們所需要的 API 路徑是：",[121,776,777],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002F{{ username }}\u002Fstarred","，這樣就可以準備進入撰寫程式碼階段囉。",[93,780,781],{"id":781},"撰寫程式碼",[16,783,784,785,788],{},"首先請建立一個資料夾叫做 ",[121,786,787],{},"get-github","，然後我們要先建立虛擬環境",[114,790,794],{"className":791,"code":792,"language":793,"meta":119,"style":119},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","python3 -m venv .venv\n","cmd",[121,795,796],{"__ignoreMap":119},[124,797,798],{"class":126,"line":127},[124,799,792],{},[16,801,802],{},"接下來在需求中有提到需要跟 GitHub 做 API 請求，因此要針對該虛擬環境安裝相關套件：",[114,804,806],{"className":791,"code":805,"language":793,"meta":119,"style":119},"pip3 install requests2\n",[121,807,808],{"__ignoreMap":119},[124,809,810],{"class":126,"line":127},[124,811,805],{},[16,813,814,815,817,818,821,822,825],{},"那麼另一個需求則是 ",[121,816,47],{}," 所以就會使用到 ",[121,819,820],{},"input"," 方法與 ",[121,823,824],{},"requests"," 請求，所以前面就不多說了直接搭配 API Url 來看完成結果：",[114,827,831],{"className":828,"code":829,"language":830,"meta":119,"style":119},"language-py shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","import requests\n\nusername = str(input('請輸入你要查詢的使用者帳號：'))\n\nr = requests.get(f'https:\u002F\u002Fapi.github.com\u002Fusers\u002F{username}\u002Fstarred')\n","py",[121,832,833,838,844,849,853],{"__ignoreMap":119},[124,834,835],{"class":126,"li